<TEXT>
YAMANOUCHI Pharmaceutical of Tokyo has taken a 29 per cent stake in Roberts
Pharmaceutical of New Jersey in a stock purchase valued at about Dollars
95m.
Yamanouchi will buy 4m newly-issued shares in Roberts at Dollars 23.84 a
