no company can realise its potential unless its people do. Education and
personal development will become one of our competitive weapons for the
future.'
Resources permitting, Laura Ashley is planning to establish an international
training centre at Carno, in Wales, where the company was founded.
Lincoln is currently group management development director at Grand
Metropolitan and has had previous management experience in the US.
