fully-franked dividend of at least 20 cents a share for the year to June 30
1992. Bunnings cut its annual dividend to 8 cents for 1990-91 from 20 cents
a year earlier.
Wesfarmers holds 19.9 per cent of Bunnings. BTR of the UK holds 24 per cent
of Bunnings acquired through its takeover of Hawker Siddeley.
